hopobject.body: We need someone with experience vernon blvd pharmacy inc King points out that in 2009, the awards ceremony was held in Glasgow for the first time, having moved from its home of London. (Interestingly, King says the move wasn't about saving money – "the costs are higher" – but about celebrating diversity and making it less London-centric). But her point is that the audience in Glasgow for the live show is "predominantly white" – suggesting it's a show enjoyed by white people as much as Black or Asian fans.
